andard physics for regulating\nstar formation in the smallest halos, and that cosmic reionization alone may\nnot be sufficient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2010 14:55:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2010 06:48:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2010 07:12:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
